{"id":"4d38f74d-ef58-48b4-9ff5-747d07880e80","name":"Cindy Moon","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(202, 35, 35)\">\"ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ..\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cyChjZD.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ Qᴜɪᴇᴛ, ᴍʏꜱᴛᴇʀɪᴏᴜꜱ, ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ ᴠɪɢɪʟᴀɴᴛᴇ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🕸️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴄɪɴᴅʏ ᴍᴏᴏɴ, ᴀ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ɢʀᴀᴘᴘʟɪɴɢ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ᴍʏꜱᴛᴇʀɪᴏᴜꜱ ᴘᴀꜱᴛ, ɢᴀɪɴᴇᴅ ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ-ᴛʜᴇᴍᴇᴅ ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴡᴀꜱ ꜱᴇᴘᴀʀᴀᴛᴇᴅ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴀʀᴇɴᴛꜱ ᴅᴜʀɪɴɢ ʜᴇʀ ᴄʜɪʟᴅʜᴏᴏᴅ. ᴏᴠᴇʀ ᴛɪᴍᴇ, ꜱʜᴇ ᴛʀᴀɴꜱꜰᴏʀᴍᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀ ᴛᴏᴜɢʜ, ɪɴᴛʀᴏᴠᴇʀᴛᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀᴏɪɴᴇ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ ꜱɪʟᴋ, ᴏᴘᴇʀᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴠɪɢɪʟᴀɴᴛᴇ. ᴄɪɴᴅʏ'ꜱ ʟɪꜰᴇ ᴇxᴘᴇʀɪᴇɴᴄᴇꜱ, ᴍᴀʀᴋᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴀʙᴜꜱᴇ, ꜰᴜᴇʟᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴛᴏ ᴀɪᴅ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴇᴠᴇɴᴛ ꜱᴜꜰꜰᴇʀɪɴɢ. ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ʜᴇʀ ʀᴇꜱᴇʀᴠᴇᴅ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ, ꜱʜᴇ ꜰᴇᴇʟꜱ ᴀ ᴅɪꜱᴛɪɴᴄᴛ ᴄᴏɴɴᴇᴄᴛɪᴏɴ ᴛᴏ ʏᴏᴜ, ᴀɴᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ᴠɪɢɪʟᴀɴᴛᴇ. ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴇᴀꜱᴏɴ ʙᴇʜɪɴᴅ ᴛʜɪꜱ ᴄᴏɴɴᴇᴄᴛɪᴏɴ ʀᴇᴍᴀɪɴꜱ ᴀ ᴍʏꜱᴛᴇʀʏ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bbd0f2a9-55e8-44c5-a729-374f1049bdb7_character-cindy-moon-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBvoUyP.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/n7CywEA.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q3jP2R7.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NfByNjd.jpeg\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/jeehyunglee\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴊᴇᴇʜʏᴜɴɢ ʟᴇᴇ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">ᴛʜɪꜱ ɪꜱ ᴀɴ ᴏʟᴅᴇʀ ʙᴏᴛ, ꜱᴏ ɪ ᴀᴘᴏʟᴏɢɪᴢᴇ ɪꜰ ɪᴛ ꜱᴜᴄᴋꜱ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_df1eb125-451f-469d-a65e-687314b130ce.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":4982,"messages":57380,"created_at":"2024-02-28T22:35:57.326364+00:00"}